A minimal, responsive single-page landing site for a lab technician. Uses only red, black, and white colors.

Contents:
- index.html: Single-page site with hero, services, and contact form
- styles.css: Styling (responsive, red/black/white only)
- script.js: Contact form alert (no backend)
- __tests__/hero.test.js: Jest test to assert the hero title is present

How to run tests:
- npm test

Notes:
- The contact form does not submit to a server; it shows an alert instead.
